snippet: Jeff Teague sank two free throws that gave Atlanta the lead with less than two minutes left, and Paul Millsap had season highs with 34 points and 15 rebounds.
abstract: NBA Roundup; Paul Millsap has season highs with 34 points and 15 rebounds as Atlanta Hawks win, 92-91, over Boston Celtics; other basketball news noted.
lead_paragraph: Jeff Teague sank two free throws that gave Atlanta the lead with less than two minutes left, and Paul Millsap had season highs with 34 points and 15 rebounds.

headline.main: Hawks Rally Over Celtics in Late Run
